data.description: Beautiful, clean & move-in ready 3 bedroom, 1 bath Bungalow with 1118 sq ft of living space & an additional 728 sq ft of space in the basement. Half of the basement is finished. On the left, is a large Recreation Room with knotty pine paneled walls & wall-to-wall carpeting. It is ideal for watching sports, movies, & your favorite TV series, as well as for playing video or board games. The right side is the laundry & utility areas which have linoleum floors & shelving for storing paint & supples. The washer & dryer are brand new (2023) & stay. The interior was just freshly painted. There are oak hardwood floors on the main floor except for the kitchen & bathroom. The bathroom was beautifully updated last summer (2022) & there is modern updated lighting & ceiling fans thru-out (2022). The living room has a floor-to-ceiling picture window that lets in lots of natural light. The eat-in kitchen has a breakfast/eating bar that seats 4 people & a 2-year old gas stove & refrigerator. There are two (2) bedrooms on the 1st floor & a bedroom on the 2nd floor with pine wood floors. The fully fenced rear yard is spacious with privacy fencing & a 2-car detached garage with garage door opener & 1-year old garage doors. The yard is ideal for anyone who has a dog or wants a safe & private place to hang out, barbecue, & have fun. The furnace is 12-years old (2011) & so is the roof (2011). The home also has glass block windows, vinyl windows, updated plumbing & electrical, etc! Violation Free!
